librarian.feywild.initial:
Hello Stranger, welcome to the Feywild, the wonderful land of fey and magic.
Have you seen a fey yet? They are a bit shy, but some tasty treats might help you gain their trust.
 Talk to me again if you like to know more about the Fey!
librarian.feywild.borrow: Ah! Curious about they Fey? You can borrow this book, it contains valuable information on the Fey Courts.
librarian.feywild.final: Here to return that book I borrowed you? No worries you can keep it for a while longer. Fair tidings!
spring_quest_pixie.feywild.summon_messag: Where Am I? Who are you? Are you tasty? Let's go on an adventure! You wanna play? I'm hungry...
spring_quest_pixie.feywild.quest_01_mess: What is that? A Cloud! No Wait, Cotton Candy! Let's make it fly!
hmm! A sheep you say? Its so fluffy I'm gonna die!
It must be lonely thou with out his friend who are all the way in the sky!
What!? It cannot fly? Flying is the best thing there is!
Wish this meep could experience the joy of flying like his friend can.
We must find away! You're smart ...
Or maybe you just have a big head.
Either way I'm sure you will find a way to make this meep fly!
summer_quest_pixie.feywild.summon_messag: Peasant, bow down in the presence of your superior! How dare you summon me like I am some sort of magician's familiar.
autumn_quest_pixie.feywild.summon_messag: Darling, what took you so long! I've been waiting for a fine specimen just like you!
winter_quest_pixie.feywild.summon_messag: Mortal. Summoning me shortens your lifespan. Now State your demand.
dwarf.feywild.dialogue: <Dwarf> Beardless friend! Talking is cheap, but ores are priceless. So, let's trade!
dwarf.feywild.trade: <Dwarf> Haha, it's always great trading with you!
dwarf.feywild.scroll: <Dwarf> Haha, I like your style. Tell me if you need anything.
message.feywild.dwarf_blacksmith: Use this scroll on a Dwarven Anvil to summon your Dwarven friend.
message.feywild.autumn_pixie: A summoning scroll for a Autumn Pixie
